{"tid":2369936,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《CHEF》 真人版 料理界李小龍 江振誠《初心》","createTime":"2021-01-17T14:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T15:06:12.000Z","uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea17e63dd00f92da0e82b7efef6e1536fdb4416","tid":2369936,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CKJEkuiHt5h/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKJEkuiHt5h%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=32686583\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKJEkuiHt5h%2F&h=2db38ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CKJEkuiHt5h/</a><br />\n<strong>江振誠《初心》<br />\nAndr&eacute; &amp; his olive tree</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/138364991_2446025649025923_8656674308237468986_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=pyM1o0ZPxUwAX9AH15L&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=82fa2fdc2aa375e8745e2c06305424fc&amp;oe=602950F0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F138364991_2446025649025923_8656674308237468986_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DpyM1o0ZPxUwAX9AH15L%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D82fa2fdc2aa375e8745e2c06305424fc%26oe%3D602950F0&h=9eacc783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由江振誠（Andr&eacute; Chiang）主理的「RAW」，被譽為台灣最難訂位的餐廳之一。44歲的Andr&eacute;亦可算是最具代表性的亞洲廚師之一，除了是台灣史上第一位摘下米芝蓮星星的主廚、還是同時榮獲全球最佳150位名廚、亞洲50最佳餐廳，盛極一時更被外國名廚戲謔「料理界李小龍」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.vogue.com.tw/photos/5fa8f11dcb3310b394458997/16:9/w_1920,c_limit/AndreStills__DSF2062_edit.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.vogue.com.tw%2Fphotos%2F5fa8f11dcb3310b394458997%2F16%3A9%2Fw_1920%2Cc_limit%2FAndreStills__DSF2062_edit.png&h=1a1e6f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNetflix新上映的的紀錄片《初心》耗時兩年完成，近距離紀錄江振在2017年毅然結束新加坡米芝蓮二星餐廳「Restaurant ANDR&Eacute;」，退回所有星星，決心告別新加坡重回台灣的心路歷程。急流勇退絕不容易，江振誠瀟灑放棄世俗名利，敬佩之意令人油然而生，紀錄片拍出來感情真摯不造作，令人真的感受到江師傅的「初心」。<br />\n<br />\n在一次偶然機會之下，有幸到江振誠主理的「江川月」用膳，先不說每道菜如何精緻匠心，但整個用餐體驗是令人耳目一新，成功將美饌昇華至另一層次。江師傅力臻完美、一絮不苟的追求，都可以在食材、烹調、員工、裝潢、甚至是菜單的設計都全面反映出來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.asiatatler.com/asiatatler/i/tw/2020/07/31161100-30175219-dsf6988-article-1200x800_cover_1200x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.asiatatler.com%2Fasiatatler%2Fi%2Ftw%2F2020%2F07%2F31161100-30175219-dsf6988-article-1200x800_cover_1200x800.jpg&h=0ccc0f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再令我想起是2014年的《滋味旅程》（Chef），由拯救了Marvel的鬼才導演Jon Favreau自編自導自演，講述是一個名廚為找入行的初心，更有Scarlett Johansson、Robert Downey Jr.客串，當中的人情味、父子情更之令人動容。看《初心》，異曲同工，不過更是真人真事，江振誠對食物的執著，員工、妻子、母親對最真實的情感，以紀錄片形式令人感受更深。<br />\n<br />\n飲水思源說起來很簡單，「初心」甚至是我們高官最愛用的說辭。但江振誠卻真正回到家鄉台灣，以行動表達對寶島珍重，讓大家了解台灣文化，對台灣食材感到驕傲。愛不是字上談兵，做啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qhPFet157WA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqhPFet157WA&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=ad2e257a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qhPFet157WA</a><br />\n各位啱睇不妨俾個like，得閒睇完戲會打下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=15f58eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=6de79ad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk</a>"},{"pid":"d23f5a3b42ff86bc72270fb9870ed26133cf6a4a","tid":2369936,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAAWvBx8YXQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeAAWvBx8YXQ&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=85d6fde8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAAWvBx8YXQ</a><br />\n<br />\n佢屋企勁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3e046a3adeb982bc7763007730d5daaf968e88","tid":2369936,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p-zdrFABnS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp-zdrFABnS4&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=08307181\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p-zdrFABnS4</a>"}]}